On Fri, 29 Oct 2004, Mike Charnoky wrote:

> After checking compression several times and doing the oil squirt, I did adjust
> the valves (hydraulics) and test again.  #3 is going, going...

if you keep losing the same cyl something somewhere is wrong, fix that or
you will keep losing valves, possibly the intake runner to #3 is partially
blocked giving that cyl a lean condition?  or an air leak in that runner??
 >
> Our new house doesn't even have a driveway, let alone a garage, and I really
