and don't have a driveway etc.   BUT I have rented a nearby garage to
store parts in and work on the bus when needed.   my bus needs some work
on it too. and my house is only part shingled, gotta get both done by real
cold weather.

> the time for this project.  Maybe you can slap on a new head in a few hours, but
