> the second time.

first time is the hardest.

> I've been at this juncture before, and I've put thousands of dollars into this

and you will put that much more into anything else you get.   pick up a
junker for the spare car and don't give your hard earned $$$ to the next
guy to get your bus....your almost there.

> bus already.  Time for me to move on.  I just want to know how long I can get by
